data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT, SELLER IS VERY MOTIVATED!!! Extraordinarily Charming Home in Plant City! GREAT LOCATION! This MOVE IN READY House is the perfect starter first time home buyers. The House has 1033sqft, 3 bedrooms 2 FULL bathrooms and 1 car garage. BRAND NEW Vinyl Waterproof floors throughout the house, The bathrooms have BRAND NEW toilets, Mirrors, vanities and sinks, New light fixtures and ceiling fans, freshly inside paint. The Kitchen Microwave is Brand new and the Fridge was recently purchased. Large backyard for you to gather with your friends and family. JUST a 3 minute drive to Downtown Plant City, close to a park, shopping, restaurants, and very easy access to I-4.
